description: The KraneShares MSCI One Belt One Road ETF (ticker: OBOR) seeks to provide investment results that track the price and yield performance of the MSCI Global China Infrastructure Exposure Index. The Index aims to identify potential beneficiaries of the One Belt One Road initiative based on how their geography, revenue, and sector attributes align with the broad theme. OBOR seeks to capture the economic growth and monetize the potential upside for the companies involved in China’s One Belt One Road initiative.
name: KraneShares MSCI One Belt One Road Index ETF
